This paper is likely to belong to the category of Computational Linguistics (cs.CL) as it deals with Chinese character embedding and word segmentation. It also involves the use of neural networks, which falls under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI), and Neural and Evolutionary Computing (cs.NE). Additionally, the paper involves the evaluation of the proposed method, which could fall under the sub-category of Information Retrieval (cs.IR).
